title: EYL #150 Ryan Leslie & Hill Harper Talk Stocks, Bitcoin, & Wealth
itunes:title: EYL #150 Ryan Leslie & Hill Harper Talk Stocks, Bitcoin, & Wealth
description:
On episode 150, we’re sharing a highlight from Investfest, our conversation with two of the brightest minds that we have had the honor of coming across. Ryan Leslie is a business, investing, and musical genius. 


He spoke about his amazing stock portfolio, being an early adaptor of Cryptocurrency because of an issue with the government, how he revolutionized music, and more. 


Hill Harper is a legendary actor, entrepreneur, and philanthropist. He discussed Cryptocurrency, the Blockchain, updates to his Black Wall Street Crypto wallet, wealth building, and more. #bitcoin #RyanLeslie #stocks #hillharper
